{"tid":1814945,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"元朗區議會組委員會調查721","createTime":"2020-01-07T07:19:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T08:47:12.000Z","uid":253773,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8986142a40fd62617d1aa4f64d7143578d12cd36","tid":1814945,"uid":253773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:19:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/07/151852_6991d410b1a15bec8179d8d97eca0114.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F07%2F151852_6991d410b1a15bec8179d8d97eca0114.jpeg&h=6aac1521&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2020年，新一屆區議會陸續開會。喺元朗區議會第一次特別會議上，民主派區議員聯合動議，就7.21元朗站有白衣人無差別襲擊市民一事，成立工作小組。<br />\n<br />\n喺所有鄉事派區議員離席底下，呢個動議得到33票贊成、無人反對或者棄權而獲得通過。  <br />\n<br />\n抗爭運動差唔多過咗六個月，但大家都冇忘記發生過嘅事。由人民選出嚟嘅代議士，亦開始喺區議會反映民意。傷痛嘅回憶未必想再記起，但喺公義得到彰顯之前，我哋唔會忘記。<br />\n<br />\n原圖來源： Tommy Cheung 張秀賢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40fdf7df6afebeeebb801dfeba7fa495f0b86169","tid":1814945,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:22:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b01af94378a486ce8f039c3fb2e314fb5bc8a07","tid":1814945,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T08:47:12.000Z","msg":"元朗區議會召開特別會議，討論721元朗站襲擊事件，會上有議員動議成立工作小組徹查事件，有鄉事派議員認為應擴大調查範圍至反修例事件中所有發生在元朗的暴力事件，包括調查示威者破壞商店等行為，但多名民主派議員反對，主席黃偉賢亦說，應交由小組成立後，再決定是否調整有關工作範圍。<br />\n<br />\n動議最終獲得大比數通過，並由張秀賢及伍健偉分別自動當選為小組正副主席。<br />\n<br />\n會議其後進入討論成立獨立調查委員會的議程，<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">多名鄉事派議員離場。</span></em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}